folder: Knapp Street & Avenue X, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Knapp Street, north from and across Avenue X. In the foreground are W. P. A. workmen near Shell Bank Creek. Across the creek, on the right, are a group of dwellings
fronting on Allen Avenue.
July. 1935
Views 1,2
Works Progress Administration
Five Boroughs Project
